Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me help you\Nmake your wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.\NThe boys are here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it now.\NArmony's alchemy never failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just dormant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She may have become\Na great alchemist indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But if... if you die,\Nthen that's the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.68,0:01:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to cry, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:02:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
